<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>How It Works - Wearable Device</title>
    <style>

body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        header nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }
        header nav a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bf8RqZBzVKQ/maxresdefault.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 70vh;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .steps {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .step {
            text-align: center;
            width: 30%;
        }
        .step img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .step h3 {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .step p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .video-section {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }
        .video-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .video-section iframe {
            width: 80%;
            height: 400px;
        }
        .faq-section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            background-color: #e2e2e2;
        }
        .faq-section h2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .faq {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .faq h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .faq p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #555;
        }
        .cta-section {
            background-color: #f04e23;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .cta-section a {
            background-color: white;
            color: #f04e23;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #222;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>How It Works</h1>
        <p>Simple steps to navigate confidently with our device.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="steps">
        <div class="step">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Wear the Device">
            <h3>Step 1: Wear the Device</h3>
            <p>Comfortably wear the device like a regular accessory.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.MgA6W5FtSczASp2m46yhtwHaHa?w=156&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="Activate the App">
            <h3>Step 2: Activate the App</h3>
            <p>Sync with our mobile app to enhance navigation features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
            <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.6er5Dd1riBumvUWHg_uVbQHaHX?w=167&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="Navigate Safely">
            <h3>Step 3: Navigate Safely</h3>
            <p>Receive real-time audio guidance and haptic feedback.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="video-section">
        <h2>Watch How It Works</h2>
        <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/your-video-id" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="faq">
            <h4>How do I set up the device?</h4>
            <p>Simply pair the device with the mobile app via Bluetooth and follow the on-screen instructions to configure settings.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq">
            <h4>Does the device work in all weather conditions?</h4>
            <p>Yes, the device is weather-resistant and can function in rain, snow, and high temperatures.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq">
            <h4>How do I charge the device?</h4>
            <p>The device comes with a charging dock. Place the device on the dock, and it will charge fully in about 2 hours.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Start Navigating with Confidence</h2>
        <a href="#">Get Started Now</a>
    </section>

   

</body>
</html>
